      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LADY LESLIE (1) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 407m behind Slick Ram (24.54) in a Mix 5. The form out of last race has been strong. Can discover winning form. GO SEEK IZRA (2) finds it hard to break through. Finished in the money last time though when third (24.04) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Bold showing expected. HARA'S FONZIE (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (24.36) in a Mix 5 at this track. Has a good record here including five wins. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. In the mix. SORSOGON SMILE (6) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three at this track and distance most recently.",
